# WR Smile and Supplies - Stock & Billing Web App

This is a simple and responsive web app for managing shop stock and generating bills for WR Smile and Supplies.

## 🔧 Features
- Add/Edit/Delete Products
- Manage Inventory
- Create Bills with Cart
- Responsive Design

## 📁 Files Included
- `index.html` – Main UI (with shop details)
- `style.css` – Optional styling
- `script.js` – JavaScript logic
- `README.md` – This file

## 🚀 How to Use
1. Save all files in a folder named `wr-smile-shop`.
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.
3. To host online:
   - Push to GitHub and enable **GitHub Pages**
   - Or deploy via [Netlify](https://netlify.com)  or [Vercel](https://vercel.com) 